## 3. Overall logic

## 3.1 Main flows

1. **Code** and **technical content** are versioned on **GitHub**.
2. **n8n** collects, transforms, or publishes flows useful to the ecosystem.
3. **Public websites** are served by **Apache2** on the **LWS VPS**.
4. **Uptime-Kuma** monitors the exposed FQDNs.
5. **Wiki + Kanboard** form the documentation / project execution pair.
6. The **Local LLM DUO Lab** remains isolated, local, and dedicated to LLM experimentation.

## 3.2 Local LLM-specific chain

```text
Web-UI Management
   ↓
Apache SRV + Proxy (SRV3)
   ↓
Virtual Host (SRV3)
   ↓
Orchestrator Python (SRV3)
   ├─→ llama.cpp Engine (SRV3) → KUZAI LLM Model
   └─→ llama.cpp Engine (SRV4) → DARKAI LLM Model
   ↓
System Prompt / Turns / Fine Tuning / Transcript
```

